<body>
<div class='container'>
<h1>Introducing PanelView Sections</h1>
<p>
PanelView sections provide the ability to generate dynamic WebView content using .rsp or .jssp pages. They can have an optional menubar at the top. </br></br>
 Clicking a menuitem will select a panel by animating it into place.</br></br>
 The contents of the panel can be generated dynamically suring the animation.</br></br>
</p>
<p>
<%
	? "Hello world at " + time() + " from panel1.rsp"
%>
</p>
</div>
